Package net.xqhs.flash.core.agent

Interface AgentEvent.AgentEventHandler

  • Enclosing class:
    AgentEvent
    public static interface AgentEvent.AgentEventHandler
    The interface should be implemented by a class that can handle agent events for an agent component. Each AgentShardCore instance is able to register, for each event, an event handler.

    The class also contains enumerations relevant to event handling: event types ( AgentEvent.AgentEventType) and types of sequences for events (AgentEvent.AgentSequenceType).

    Author:
    Andrei Olaru

    • Method Summary

      All Methods Instance Methods Abstract Methods 
      Modifier and Type Method Description
      void handleEvent​(AgentEvent event)
      The method is invoked whenever the event is posted to the CompositeAgent the component is part of.

    • Method Detail

      • handleEvent

        void handleEvent​(AgentEvent event)
        The method is invoked whenever the event is posted to the CompositeAgent the component is part of.

        The handlers in various components will be invoked (through the method in AgentShardCore) in the order specified by the AgentEvent.AgentSequenceType associated with the event.

        Parameters:
        event - - the event that occurred.
